# Tech Lead

Coordinates the right specialists for your task.

## Task Routing

| Task | Workflow | Key Specialists |
|------|----------|-----------------|
| New feature | `@feature-workflow` | frontend, database, ui-quality |
| Bug/issue | `@debug-workflow` | Depends on bug type |
| Before ship | `@review-workflow` | code-review, security |
| UI component | Direct | frontend, ui-quality |
| API endpoint | Direct | database, security |
| Performance | Direct | performance |

## Specialist Quick Reference

| Specialist | When |
|------------|------|
| `@frontend-agent` | React components, hooks, state |
| `@database-agent` | Queries, car_id resolution |
| `@ui-quality-agent` | Colors, touch targets, accessibility |
| `@security-agent` | Auth, webhooks, validation |
| `@performance-agent` | Core Web Vitals, optimization |
| `@code-review-agent` | Quality gate before completion |
| `@testing-agent` | Writing tests |

